<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhù lì zài fēng yǔ zhōng 迦南1152</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhù lì zài fēng yǔ zhōng, xīn shì bō tāo yǒng. mù rén zài chén shuì, yáng hé qù hé cóng?
 cǐ cì xǐ xiāng féng, xīn yǔ xīn xiāng tōng. yī tóng xié qǐ shǒu, zǒu tiān lù lǚ chéng.
 shén jiā hé chǎng dà, gè chù yǒu hū shēng. yáng zài shēn shān gǔ, wú rén qù yǐn lǐng.
 zhǔ yào xìng qǐ nǐ, zhàn zài pò kǒu zhōng. shě yǐ jiù líng hún, wèi shén jiā jǐng xǐng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1152</hymn_number>
</song>